These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, february
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, baking
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Birthday   | august  | february |
| Hobby     | baking | sudoku  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, blue
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, march
1. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Color    | mauve      | blue         |
| Birthday   | october | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, fisherman
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, boat
1. the project-manager is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Job   | fisherman | project-manager   |
| Transport       | boat  | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, punk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, september
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | punk |
| Birthday         | may | september    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
