.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, chinese
House: victorian, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |
| Nationality        | chinese  | pakistani |
| House   | victorian | ranch-style  |

